name: GapTech
description: Living in a third world country is very exciting. One of them is behind technology, where all of us are a potential market for technology producing countries to market their products. Here technology is easy to swallow without understanding the basis of why the technology was created. Like today, where there is a very significant change in people's behavior. Viral for example, where everyone wants things that are made to go viral because it can increase some value. These values turned out to have a very significant effect on many things, but on the other hand negates some values. It's really interesting everything that's going on and I'm just sitting around drinking almost stale tea, writing all this.
